# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Changelog for Mail::ExpandAliases
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Version 0.49                                              July 1, 2010
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Fixed a bug in exists() that would have been caught with better tests.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Version 0.48                                              July 1, 2010
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Added check and exists methods.  check() returns the literall,
  non-recursively-expanded alias value, and exists returns a boolean
  indicating whether an alias is defined in a file.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Version 0.45                                              (Unreleased)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Added patch from Thomas Kishel <tom@kishel.net>, which adds a method
  that returns a list of all of the aliases in the aliase file.

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Version 0.44                                        September 22, 2004 
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Initial import from old CVS repository.
